divs: Sighting DetailsIt was hovering over Daniel Webster Western Beltway, Winter Garden, FL 34787 it had several colors and was hovering very low. I saw it around 9PM looked like a plane from a distance but I went right under it and it had no sound what so ever. I tried taking a picture but nothing showed up on camera! I lost sight because I drove away.
